msgid "Connect to dev server"
msgstr "Koneksikan ke server dev"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Authenticate with the Spwig shop and create a development session.\n"
"\n"
"    **Authentication**: Basic auth with admin credentials\n"
"\n"
"    Returns a session token for subsequent API calls.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Autentikasi dengan toko Spwig dan buat sesi pengembangan. "
"**Autentikasi**: Autentikasi dasar dengan kredensial admin Mengembalikan "
"token sesi untuk panggilan API berikutnya.\n"
"    "

msgid "Session created successfully"
msgstr "Sesi berhasil dibuat"

msgid "Authentication failed"
msgstr "Autentikasi gagal"

msgid "Dev server not enabled"
msgstr "Server dev tidak aktif"

msgid "Disconnect from dev server"
msgstr "Putuskan koneksi dari server dev"

msgid "End the development session and cleanup resources."
msgstr "Akhirkan sesi pengembangan dan bersihkan sumber daya."

msgid "Session ended successfully"
msgstr "Sesi berhasil diakhiri"

msgid "Invalid token"
msgstr "Token tidak valid"

msgid "Get session status"
msgstr "Dapatkan status sesi"

msgid "Get current status of the development session."
msgstr "Dapatkan status saat ini dari sesi pengembangan."

msgid "Session status"
msgstr "Status sesi"

msgid "Sync theme files"
msgstr "Sinkronkan file tema"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Sync individual files from SDK to dev server.\n"
"\n"
"    Send an array of files with path, content (base64 for binary), and "
"checksum.\n"
"    Files are written to the dev theme directory and trigger appropriate "
"reload.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Sinkronkan file individu dari SDK ke server pengembangan. Kirim array "
"file dengan path, konten (base64 untuk biner), dan checksum. File akan "
"ditulis ke direktori tema pengembangan dan memicu reload yang sesuai.\n"
"    "

msgid "Files synced successfully"
msgstr "File berhasil disinkronkan"

msgid "Invalid request"
msgstr "Permintaan tidak valid"

msgid "Sync full theme archive"
msgstr "Sinkronkan arsip tema penuh"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Sync a complete theme as a ZIP archive.\n"
"\n"
"    The archive replaces the entire dev theme directory.\n"
"    Send the ZIP file as raw binary in the request body.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Sinkronkan tema lengkap sebagai arsip ZIP. Arsip menggantikan seluruh "
"direktori tema pengembangan. Kirim file ZIP sebagai biner mentah dalam tubuh "
"permintaan.\n"
"    "

msgid "Theme synced successfully"
msgstr "Tema berhasil disinkronkan"

msgid "Invalid archive"
msgstr "Arsip tidak valid"

msgid "Watch for reload events"
msgstr "Pantau acara reload"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Server-Sent Events stream for hot reload notifications.\n"
"\n"
"    Events:\n"
"    - `css`: CSS-only reload (no page refresh)\n"
"    - `full`: Full page reload\n"
"    - `keepalive`: Connection keepalive\n"
"\n"
"    Inject a small JS snippet in dev mode to listen to this stream.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Aliran Server-Sent Events untuk notifikasi hot reload. Acara: - `css`: "
"reload hanya CSS (tanpa refresh halaman) - `full`: reload halaman penuh - "
"`keepalive`: menjaga koneksi. Sisipkan snippet JS kecil dalam mode "
"pengembangan untuk mendengarkan aliran ini.\n"
"    "

