msgid "Get header template for builder"
msgstr "Dapatkan template header untuk pembangun"

msgid ""
"\n"
"        Load a header template with all widget placements for the visual "
"builder.\n"
"\n"
"        Returns the header configuration including zones and all placed "
"widgets\n"
"        with their merged configurations (base config + overrides).\n"
"\n"
"        **Authentication:** Admin user required\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        Muat template header dengan semua penempatan widget untuk pembangun "
"visual. Mengembalikan konfigurasi header termasuk zona dan semua widget yang "
"ditempatkan dengan konfigurasinya yang digabungkan (konfigurasi dasar + "
"penimbal). **Autentikasi:** Diperlukan pengguna admin\n"
"        "

msgid "Header template data with widget placements"
msgstr "Data template header dengan penempatan widget"

msgid "Update header template"
msgstr "Perbarui template header"

msgid ""
"\n"
"        Update header template properties.\n"
"\n"
"        Supports partial updates - only provided fields will be modified.\n"
"\n"
"        **Authentication:** Admin user required\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        Perbarui properti template header. Mendukung pembaruan parsial - "
"hanya bidang yang disediakan yang akan diubah. **Autentikasi:** Diperlukan "
"pengguna admin\n"
"        "

msgid "Header updated successfully"
msgstr "Header berhasil diperbarui"

msgid "Invalid request data"
msgstr "Data permintaan tidak valid"

msgid "Publish header template"
msgstr "Publikasikan template header"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Publish the current draft of a header template, making it live on the "
"storefront.\n"
"\n"
"    Copies draft_data to published_data and updates the published_at "
"timestamp.\n"
"\n"
"    **Authentication:** Admin user required\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Publikasikan draf header saat ini sehingga menjadi aktif di toko online. "
"Salin draft_data ke published_data dan perbarui timestamp published_at. "
"**Autentikasi:** Diperlukan pengguna admin\n"
"    "

msgid "Header published successfully"
msgstr "Header berhasil dipublikasikan"

msgid "Discard header draft changes"
msgstr "Buang perubahan draf header"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Discard all unpublished changes and revert draft to the published "
"state.\n"
"\n"
"    **Authentication:** Admin user required\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Batalkan semua perubahan yang belum diterbitkan dan kembalikan draf ke "
"keadaan yang sudah diterbitkan. **Autentikasi:** Diperlukan pengguna admin\n"
"    "

msgid "Draft discarded, reverted to published state"
msgstr "Draf dibuang, dikembalikan ke status terbit"

msgid "Get footer template for builder"
msgstr "Dapatkan template footer untuk pembangun"

msgid ""
"\n"
"        Load a footer template with all widget placements for the visual "
"builder.\n"
"\n"
"        Returns the footer configuration including zones and all placed "
"widgets\n"
"        with their merged configurations (base config + overrides).\n"
"\n"
"        **Authentication:** Admin user required\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        Muat template footer dengan semua penempatan widget untuk pembangun "
"visual. Mengembalikan konfigurasi footer termasuk zona dan semua widget yang "
"ditempatkan beserta konfigurasinya yang digabungkan (konfigurasi dasar + "
"penimbalan). **Autentikasi:** Diperlukan pengguna admin\n"
"        "

msgid "Footer template data with widget placements"
msgstr "Data template footer dengan penempatan widget"

msgid "Update footer template"
msgstr "Perbarui template footer"

msgid ""
"\n"
"        Update footer template properties.\n"
"\n"
"        Supports partial updates - only provided fields will be modified.\n"
"\n"
"        **Authentication:** Admin user required\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        Perbarui properti template footer. Mendukung pembaruan parsial - "
"hanya bidang yang disediakan yang akan diubah. **Otentikasi:** Pengguna "
"admin diperlukan\n"
"        "

msgid "Footer updated successfully"
msgstr "Footer berhasil diperbarui"

msgid "Publish footer template"
msgstr "Publikasikan template footer"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Publish the current draft of a footer template, making it live on the "
"storefront.\n"
"\n"
"    Copies draft_data to published_data and updates the published_at "
"timestamp.\n"
"\n"
"    **Authentication:** Admin user required\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Publikasikan draf saat ini dari template footer, sehingga menjadi aktif "
"di toko online. Salin draft_data ke published_data dan perbarui timestamp "
"published_at. **Otentikasi:** Pengguna admin diperlukan\n"
"    "

msgid "Footer published successfully"
msgstr "Footer berhasil diterbitkan"

msgid "Discard footer draft changes"
msgstr "Buang perubahan draf footer"

msgid "Create widget placement"
msgstr "Buat penempatan widget"

msgid ""
"\n"
"        Add a widget to a header or footer zone.\n"
"\n"
"        Must specify either `header_id` or `footer_id` (not both).\n"
"\n"
"        **Authentication:** Admin user required\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        Tambahkan widget ke zona header atau footer. Harus menentukan salah "
"satu `header_id` atau `footer_id` (bukan keduanya). **Otentikasi:** Pengguna "
"admin diperlukan\n"
"        "

msgid "Widget placement created"
msgstr "Penempatan widget berhasil dibuat"

msgid "Update widget placement"
msgstr "Perbarui penempatan widget"

msgid ""
"\n"
"        Update an existing widget placement.\n"
"\n"
"        Supports partial updates for zone, order, is_active, and "
"override_config.\n"
"\n"
"        **Authentication:** Admin user required\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        Perbarui penempatan widget yang sudah ada. Mendukung pembaruan "
"parsial untuk zona, urutan, is_active, dan override_config. **Autentikasi:** "
"Diperlukan pengguna admin\n"
"        "

msgid "Placement updated"
msgstr "Penempatan diperbarui"

msgid "Placement not found"
msgstr "Penempatan tidak ditemukan"

msgid "Delete widget placement"
msgstr "Hapus penempatan widget"

msgid ""
"\n"
"        Remove a widget from its zone.\n"
"\n"
"        **Authentication:** Admin user required\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        Hapus widget dari zona-nya. **Autentikasi:** Pengguna admin "
"diperlukan\n"
"        "

msgid "Placement deleted"
msgstr "Penempatan dihapus"

msgid "Reorder widget placements"
msgstr "Atur ulang urutan penempatan widget"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Update the order of multiple widget placements within a zone.\n"
"\n"
"    Accepts a list of placement IDs with their new order values.\n"
"    All updates are performed atomically in a single transaction.\n"
"\n"
"    **Authentication:** Admin user required\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Perbarui urutan penempatan widget yang berada dalam satu zona. Menerima "
"daftar ID penempatan beserta nilai urutan baru. Semua pembaruan dilakukan "
"secara atomik dalam satu transaksi. **Autentikasi:** Diperlukan pengguna "
"admin\n"
"    "

msgid "Placements reordered"
msgstr "Penempatan telah diurutkan ulang"

msgid "Get widget library"
msgstr "Dapatkan perpustakaan widget"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Get all available widgets for the builder's widget library panel.\n"
"\n"
"    Returns widgets grouped by type (logo, menu, search, cart, etc.).\n"
"    Each widget includes its base configuration and visibility settings.\n"
"\n"
"    **Authentication:** Admin user required\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Dapatkan semua widget yang tersedia untuk panel perpustakaan widget "
"pembuat. Mengembalikan widget yang dikelompokkan berdasarkan tipe (logo, "
"menu, pencarian, keranjang, dll.). Setiap widget mencakup konfigurasi dasar "
"dan pengaturan visibilitasnya. **Autentikasi:** Diperlukan pengguna admin\n"
"    "

msgid "Widgets grouped by type"
msgstr "Widget dikelompokkan berdasarkan tipe"

msgid "Get widget property schemas"
msgstr "Dapatkan skema properti widget"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Get JSON schemas defining widget property panel configuration.\n"
"\n"
"    Schemas are loaded from JSON files in `design/templates/design/widgets/"
"`.\n"
"    Each schema defines the property groups and fields for a widget type's\n"
"    configuration panel in the visual builder.\n"
"\n"
"    **Authentication:** Admin user required\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Dapatkan skema JSON yang mendefinisikan konfigurasi panel properti "
"widget. Skema dimuat dari file JSON di `design/templates/design/widgets/`. "
"Setiap skema mendefinisikan kelompok properti dan bidang untuk panel "
"konfigurasi tipe widget di pembangun visual. **Autentikasi:** Diperlukan "
"pengguna admin\n"
"    "

msgid "Widget schemas keyed by type"
msgstr "Skema widget yang dikunci berdasarkan tipe"

msgid "Get preset templates"
msgstr "Dapatkan template bawaan"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Get available preset templates for headers or footers.\n"
"\n"
"    Presets are pre-configured templates that can be cloned to create\n"
"    new headers/footers with predefined layouts and widget configurations.\n"
"\n"
"    **Authentication:** Admin user required\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Dapatkan preset template yang tersedia untuk header atau footer. Preset "
"adalah template yang sudah dikonfigurasi sebelumnya yang dapat dikloning "
"untuk membuat header/footer baru dengan tata letak dan konfigurasi widget "
"yang telah ditentukan. **Otorisasi:** Diperlukan pengguna admin\n"
"    "

msgid "Type of template: \"header\" or \"footer\""
msgstr "Jenis template: \"header\" atau \"footer\""

msgid "List of preset templates"
msgstr "Daftar template bawaan"

msgid "Invalid template_type"
msgstr "Tipe template tidak valid"

msgid "Clone a preset template"
msgstr "Duplikat template bawaan"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Create a new header or footer by cloning a preset template.\n"
"\n"
"    Copies all widget placements and configurations from the preset.\n"
"    The new template will not be marked as default or preset.\n"
"\n"
"    **Authentication:** Admin user required\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Buat header atau footer baru dengan mengklon preset template. Menyalin "
"semua penempatan dan konfigurasi widget dari preset. Template baru tidak "
"akan ditandai sebagai default atau preset. **Otorisasi:** Diperlukan "
"pengguna admin\n"
"    "

msgid "ID of the preset to clone"
msgstr "ID preset yang akan dikloning"

msgid "New template created from preset"
msgstr "Template baru dibuat dari preset"

msgid "Invalid request or clone failed"
msgstr "Permintaan tidak valid atau cloning gagal"

msgid "Preset not found"
msgstr "Template bawaan tidak ditemukan"

msgid "List available menus"
msgstr "Daftar menu yang tersedia"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Get all active menus for widget configuration dropdowns.\n"
"\n"
"    Used by the menu widget to select which menu to display.\n"
"\n"
"    **Authentication:** Admin user required\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Dapatkan semua menu aktif untuk dropdown konfigurasi widget. Digunakan "
"oleh widget menu untuk memilih menu mana yang akan ditampilkan. **Otorisasi:"
"** Diperlukan pengguna admin\n"
"    "

msgid "List of active menus"
msgstr "Daftar menu aktif"

msgid "Duplicate header template"
msgstr "Duplikat template header"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Create a copy of an existing header template.\n"
"\n"
"    Copies all settings and widget placements. The new header will not\n"
"    be marked as default or preset.\n"
"\n"
"    **Authentication:** Admin user required\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Buat salinan dari template header yang sudah ada. Menyalin semua "
"pengaturan dan penempatan widget. Header baru tidak akan ditandai sebagai "
"default atau preset. **Autentikasi:** Diperlukan pengguna admin\n"
"    "

msgid "Header duplicated successfully"
msgstr "Header berhasil diduplikat"

msgid "Duplication failed"
msgstr "Duplikasi gagal"

msgid "Delete header template"
msgstr "Hapus template header"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Delete a header template after validation checks.\n"
"\n"
"    Will fail if:\n"
"    - The header is the site default\n"
"    - The header is in use by pages\n"
"\n"
"    Widget placements are deleted via cascade.\n"
"\n"
"    **Authentication:** Admin user required\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Hapus template header setelah pemeriksaan validasi. Akan gagal jika: - "
"Header adalah default situs - Header sedang digunakan oleh halaman "
"Penempatan widget dihapus secara berantai. **Autentikasi:** Diperlukan "
"pengguna admin\n"
"    "

msgid "Header deleted successfully"
msgstr "Header berhasil dihapus"

msgid "Cannot delete (default or in use)"
msgstr "Tidak dapat dihapus (default atau sedang digunakan)"

msgid "Set default header"
msgstr "Atur header default"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Set a header template as the site default.\n"
"\n"
"    The previously default header will be automatically unset.\n"
"\n"
"    **Authentication:** Admin user required\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Tetapkan template header sebagai default situs. Header default "
"sebelumnya akan secara otomatis dibatalkan. **Autentikasi:** Diperlukan "
"pengguna admin\n"
"    "

msgid "Header set as default"
msgstr "Header telah diatur sebagai default"

msgid "Get site logo for builder"
msgstr "Dapatkan logo situs untuk pembuat"

msgid ""
"\n"
"        Get the current site logo URL and metadata for the header/footer "
"builder.\n"
"\n"
"        Used by the logo widget to display the site logo when \"Use Site "
"Logo\" is enabled.\n"
"\n"
"        **Authentication:** Admin user required\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        Dapatkan URL dan metadata logo situs saat ini untuk pembangun header/"
"footer. Digunakan oleh widget logo untuk menampilkan logo situs ketika "
"\"Gunakan Logo Situs\" diaktifkan. **Autentikasi:** Diperlukan pengguna "
"admin\n"
"        "

msgid "Site logo data"
msgstr "Data logo situs"

msgid "Update site logo from widget"
msgstr "Perbarui logo situs dari widget"

msgid ""
"\n"
"        Update the site logo from a logo widget upload.\n"
"\n"
"        When a merchant uploads a new logo in the header/footer builder logo "
"widget,\n"
"        this endpoint allows syncing that logo to the site settings.\n"
"\n"
"        **Authentication:** Admin user required\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        Perbarui logo situs dari unggah widget logo. Ketika pedagang "
"mengunggah logo baru di widget logo pembangun header/footer, endpoint ini "
"memungkinkan sinkronisasi logo tersebut ke pengaturan situs. **Autentikasi:"
"** Diperlukan pengguna admin\n"
"        "

msgid "Site logo updated"
msgstr "Logo situs telah diperbarui"

msgid "Missing asset_id"
msgstr "asset_id tidak ditemukan"

msgid "Asset or settings not found"
msgstr "Aset atau pengaturan tidak ditemukan"

msgid "Render widget preview"
msgstr "Render pratinjau widget"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Render a widget with given configuration for real-time preview in the "
"builder.\n"
"\n"
"    Uses the same Django templates as the storefront to ensure visual "
"consistency.\n"
"    This ensures the preview always matches the actual appearance.\n"
"\n"
"    **Authentication:** Admin user required\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Render widget dengan konfigurasi yang diberikan untuk pratinjau real-"
"time di pembangun. Menggunakan template Django yang sama seperti toko depan "
"untuk memastikan konsistensi visual. Ini memastikan pratinjau selalu sesuai "
"dengan tampilan sebenarnya. **Autentikasi:** Diperlukan pengguna admin\n"
"    "

msgid "Rendered widget HTML"
msgstr "HTML widget yang dirender"

msgid "Missing widget_type parameter"
msgstr "Parameter widget_type tidak ditemukan"

msgid "List all menus"
msgstr "Daftar semua menu"

msgid ""
"\n"
"        Returns all menus for the store, ordered by location and name.\n"
"\n"
"        **Use Cases:**\n"
"        - Populate menu selector dropdowns in builder interfaces\n"
"        - List available menus in admin dashboard\n"
"\n"
"        **Authentication:** Staff session required\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        Mengembalikan semua menu untuk toko, diurutkan berdasarkan lokasi "
"dan nama. **Penggunaan:** - Mengisi dropdown pemilih menu di antarmuka "
"pembangun - Menampilkan daftar menu yang tersedia di dashboard admin "
"**Autentikasi:** Session staf diperlukan\n"
"        "

msgid "Not authenticated"
msgstr "Tidak terautentikasi"

msgid "Permission denied - staff access required"
msgstr "Akses ditolak - akses staf diperlukan"

msgid "Create a new menu"
msgstr "Buat menu baru"

msgid ""
"\n"
"        Creates a new navigation menu.\n"
"\n"
"        **Use Cases:**\n"
"        - Create new menu from menu builder\n"
"        - Programmatically add menus\n"
"\n"
"        **Authentication:** Staff session required\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        Membuat menu navigasi baru. **Penggunaan:** - Membuat menu baru dari "
"pembangun menu - Menambahkan menu secara program **Autentikasi:** Session "
"staf diperlukan\n"
"        "

msgid "Validation error"
msgstr "Kesalahan validasi"

msgid "Get menu with full item tree"
msgstr "Dapatkan menu dengan pohon item lengkap"

msgid ""
"\n"
"        Returns complete menu details including all items in a nested tree "
"structure.\n"
"\n"
"        The `items_tree` field contains menu items with their children "
"nested,\n"
"        suitable for rendering in the visual menu builder.\n"
"\n"
"        **Use Cases:**\n"
"        - Load menu data for visual builder\n"
"        - Retrieve complete menu structure for rendering\n"
"\n"
"        **Authentication:** Staff session required\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        Mengembalikan detail menu lengkap termasuk semua item dalam struktur "
"pohon bersarang. Bidang `items_tree` berisi item menu dengan anaknya yang "
"bersarang, cocok untuk dirender di pembangun menu visual. **Kasus Penggunaan:"
"** - Memuat data menu untuk pembangun visual - Mengambil struktur menu "
"lengkap untuk rendering **Autentikasi:** Sesi staf diperlukan\n"
"        "

msgid "Menu not found"
msgstr "Menu tidak ditemukan"

msgid "Update menu settings"
msgstr "Perbarui pengaturan menu"

msgid ""
"\n"
"        Updates menu properties (name, location, display type, styling).\n"
"\n"
"        Does NOT update menu items - use the menu items endpoints for that.\n"
"\n"
"        **Authentication:** Staff session required\n"
"\n"
"        **Side Effects:**\n"
"        - Clears cached menu renders\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        Memperbarui properti menu (nama, lokasi, tipe tampilan, gaya). TIDAK "
"memperbarui item menu - gunakan endpoint item menu untuk itu. **Autentikasi:"
"** Session staf diperlukan **Efek Samping:** - Menghapus render menu yang "
"disimpan sebelumnya\n"
"        "

msgid "Partially update menu settings"
msgstr "Perbarui sebagian pengaturan menu"

msgid ""
"\n"
"        Partially updates menu properties.\n"
"\n"
"        **Authentication:** Staff session required\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        Memperbarui sebagian properti menu. **Otentikasi:** Sesi staf "
"diperlukan\n"
"        "

msgid "Delete menu"
msgstr "Hapus menu"

msgid ""
"\n"
"        Deletes a menu and all its items.\n"
"\n"
"        **Authentication:** Staff session required\n"
"\n"
"        **Warning:** This action cannot be undone.\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        Menghapus menu dan semua itemnya. **Otentikasi:** Sesi staf "
"diperlukan **Peringatan:** Tindakan ini tidak dapat dibatalkan.\n"
"        "

msgid "Menu deleted"
msgstr "Menu dihapus"

msgid "Get menu item details"
msgstr "Dapatkan detail item menu"

msgid ""
"\n"
"        Returns details of a specific menu item.\n"
"\n"
"        **Authentication:** Staff session required\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        Mengembalikan detail item menu tertentu. **Otentikasi:** Sesi staf "
"diperlukan\n"
"        "

msgid "Menu item not found"
msgstr "Item menu tidak ditemukan"

msgid "Update menu item"
msgstr "Perbarui item menu"

msgid ""
"\n"
"        Updates a menu item's properties.\n"
"\n"
"        **Authentication:** Staff session required\n"
"        "
